{"id":238125,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-上海民众第57次向市人大请愿要求诉权（组/","date":"2012-07-06T17:01:34Z","modified":"2012-07-06T17:01:34Z","title":"维权网 | 上海民众第57次向市人大请愿要求诉权（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Uo6kYIFItCU/T_cLl2wDyUI/AAAAAAAAJA8/SQdv1gDzbDE/s1600/57%E6%AC%A1SAM_0299.JPG\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a><img border=\"0\" height=\"164\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Uo6kYIFItCU/T_cLl2wDyUI/AAAAAAAAJA8/SQdv1gDzbDE/s320/57%E6%AC%A1SAM_0299.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<div> </div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，上海市民为了捍卫法律，代表</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1060</span><span>户家庭向上海市人大常委会第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">57</span><span>次请愿。请求维护国家尊严，树立正确的政府形象，清除上海司法不作为乱作为的恶习！维护社会公平正义，建设法治政府，使行政权力授予有据、行使有规、监督有效，做到依法治官、依法治权，防止行政权力的缺失和滥用，带动全社会尊重法律、遵守法律、还诉权于民。再次请求上海市人大常委会认真履行法定职责，切实行使监督“一府二院”的权力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当上访民众推荐的市民代表有赵迪迪、鲁俊、崔福芳、黄尧年、高月清等五位代表进入人大登记处登记时，负责登记保安即没有姓名又不肯告知工号的蛮横者无理找茬，非要把解决公民诉权的共性问题分解成个案。遭到在场广大市民共同的驳斥：不解决诉权，空谈案件又有何用？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另一位保安出来打圆场，把大家带到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">105</span><span>费</span><span>老师接待室等候，鲁俊见到久别的费老师，高声问费老师今天接待吗？费老师也大声回答：接待、接待。</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>代表反映久拖未决的公民诉权问题，费老师表示人大常委会也很重视，要求代表们把诉状材料带来，人大常委会研究后会督促法院合理解决。其间费老师与冯正虎通了电话互致问候，并对公民诉权关心问题各自简单发表了一点看法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>莘庄工业区代表反映上海市高院既不立案又不裁定，还多次和其它部门联合起来数次强行把失地农民抓到府春路和偏远地方关押数小时，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>当天下午一点多上海市高院又和警方联手抓捕众多失地农民关押，搜身等严重违法事件，希望费老师如实向上海市人大常委会反映这一起严重违法事件，费老师点头表示知道了。</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>临别费老师强调各位代表不必去保安处登记可直接找他信访，并请代表们把详细起诉材料带来，尽管代表们满肚委屈，但与费老师反映问题还是比较温和的，费老师也是上海市整个信访部门比较依法办事的接待员，大家也希望费老师起到桥梁作用给受屈者带来一点福音和希望。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与本次集体访请愿行动的市民代表有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">111</span><span>人签名，其名单附图。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动，请与下述市民代表联系：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524687100</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>焦东海</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13801802454</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span></span><span>俊</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13651817422</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>赵迪迪</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13482668387</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>崔福芳</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13564097383</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13042111402</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>沈佩兰</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13764885120</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>王扣玛</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13601929155</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>王蓉华</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13162424968</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>邱贵荣</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15300606275</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>刘洪贤</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524850369</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>童国菁</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13917920278</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>郑培培</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">02153963826</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>徐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span></span><span>伟</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13331866362</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>孙建敏</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13671947476</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳</span><span> </span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15026516445</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1AsWcr-Lq9E/T_cLuaTISaI/AAAAAAAAJBE/NLoKzzJhIQg/s1600/img513.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1AsWcr-Lq9E/T_cLuaTISaI/AAAAAAAAJBE/NLoKzzJhIQg/s320/img513.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fV4-QYQMc_A/T_cLxxyT33I/AAAAAAAAJBM/4URdLnbB4ZM/s1600/img514.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fV4-QYQMc_A/T_cLxxyT33I/AAAAAAAAJBM/4URdLnbB4ZM/s320/img514.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-l5xCWlmYYHU/T_cL0OeXU_I/AAAAAAAAJBU/VFTFzXMBf1s/s1600/img515.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-l5xCWlmYYHU/T_cL0OeXU_I/AAAAAAAAJBU/VFTFzXMBf1s/s320/img515.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6Fa3pobshX8/T_cL21m8OzI/AAAAAAAAJBc/tr3cJUY0rMg/s1600/img516.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-6Fa3pobsh